title: #149: Doctor Doctor (Dr. Steve Graham, @JeremyHornElite
itunes:title: Doctor Doctor with Dr. Steve Graham, Jeremy Horn
description: Dr. Steve Grraham and Jeremy Horn met me in my hotel room at the MGM to talk about what being a doctor really entails. Dr Steve, as everybody calls him, was awesome. He was completely open about the realities of his job. It's a lot different than I thought. From the hours, to the pay, to the patients, he talked about it all. And Obamacare.
